# ===== TWITTER API CREDENTIALS =====
# To obtain these credentials:
# 1. Go to https://developer.twitter.com/
# 2. Create/login to your developer account
# 3. Create a new project and app
# 4. Generate the keys and tokens below
# 5. Configure OAuth 1.0a settings in your app:
#    - Add callback URL: https://chadbattles.fun/auth/twitter-callback
#    - Add callback URL: http://localhost:5000/auth/twitter-callback
#    - Enable 3-legged OAuth
#    - Request email from users
